                                    </extent>
                                </supportDesc>
                            </objectDesc>
                            <handDesc>
                                <handNote xml:id="hand-1">Carolingian minuscule.</handNote>
                            </handDesc>
                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in brown ink.</p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="S1r" to="S1r" scheme="folios"/>: decorated initial O over 3 lines. Outlined in ink, colours smudged, but appear to have been mainly green, red and gold. Counterspace filled with flower shape with six petals; decorated initial P over 2 lines. Outlined in ink, coloured with red, green, and gold.</p>
                                </decoNote>
                            </decoDesc>
